comments: McDaniels (MIN) swipes his hand against Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) arm as they come together in the lane, and the contact affects his ability to gather the loose ball.
Towns (MIN) briefly grasps Jones Jr.'s (DAL) arm off ball before correcting.
Edwards (MIN) brings his arm toward Irving's (DAL) path and marginal contact occurs during Irving's drive to the basket.
Irving (DAL) gathers the ball and slides his pivot foot.
Powell (DAL) and Conley (MIN) mutually engage and immediately disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
At the end of the drive, Doncic (DAL) makes marginal contact with Gobert's (MIN) arm.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Gobert (MIN) is the last person to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds. The possession is correctly awarded to DAL.
Powell (DAL) establishes himself in Conley's (MIN) path and is firming up as marginal contact occurs.
Towns (MIN) and Jones Jr. (DAL) engage and immediately disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Conley (MIN) establishes himself in Doncic's (DAL) path, firming up and marginal body contact occurs as Doncic defends over the screen.
Towns (MIN) somewhat extends his leg out during his shooting motion and marginal lower body contact occurs as Doncic (DAL) contests the jump shot attempt.
Powell (DAL) establishes himself firming up against Gobert's (MIN) right side off-ball and marginal contact occurs as Gobert moves to defend the shot attempt.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Towns (MIN) is the last person to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds. The possession is correctly given to DAL.
Anderson (MIN) commits a take foul on Doncic (DAL).
Jones Jr. (DAL) jumps slightly A->B and marginal lower body contact occurs with Edwards' (MIN) extended leg during his driving shot attempt.
Conley (MIN) commits a take foul on Hardaway Jr. (DAL).
Edwards (MIN) places his bent forearm against Jones Jr. (DAL) and marginal contact occurs as Edwards releases away into his step-back move.
